---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Systems | Austin Armoto">
  <Navbar />

  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Systems</h1>

    <p class="max-w-3xl text-slate-300 text-lg mb-12">
      Selected systems and platforms I have designed, built, maintained, or operated across automation, infrastructure, and hardware-adjacent workflows.
    </p>

    <section class="space-y-8">
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-8">
        <p class="text-blue-400 mb-3">AWS • Jira • Lambda • S3 • CDK • CloudWatch</p>
        <a
          href="/systems/automated-data-platform"
          class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 block hover:text-blue-400"
        >
          Automated Data Processing Platform
        </a>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">
          Designed and implemented an event-driven workflow automation system that integrates Jira workflows,
          AWS infrastructure, backend processing services, and operational data handling.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-400">
          Reduced processing time from multiple days to roughly 30 minutes while improving visibility,
          validation, and operational handoff between teams.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-8">
        <p class="text-blue-400 mb-3">Python • Calibration • Robotics • Testing</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Calibration & Validation Tooling</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400">
          Built and maintained tooling for camera and magnetometer calibration workflows supporting autonomous systems,
          including updates for hardware revisions, testing, and regression prevention.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-8">
        <p class="text-blue-400 mb-3">Salesforce • AWS • Automation • Email Relay</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Operations Workflow Platform</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400">
          Managed Salesforce objects, flows, account configuration, and AWS-backed encrypted email relay infrastructure
          supporting operational workflows.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>